&lt;h1 id="science-expands-our-vision-of-reality"&gt;Science Expands Our Vision of Reality&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apr 28 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The multiverse is another step in this direction&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
